Basically Now

Today My Sister and I, lost our father, “Jerome”. Our Emotions have been all over the place today but if there’s something our father did right, it was create the “2” of us. We are inseparable and I’ve never had a better friend in this life than my sister Aisha. Thru the Love, The Pain, The Losses, and The Lessons. I Got You Forever Kid. Rest Easy To Our Father, The Nicest, Most Mild Manored Man I Knew. I Luv U Twin, and I Still Ain’t Mad Atcha
I have definitely had a day…… but the show must go on. I am headed to @thecheetah.atl for “Thirst” Thursday’s. If you’re out pull up on me

As I Sit Here In Tears, Thinking About Your Life, I Think About The Circumstances You Had To Navigate Your Way Thru In Order To Just Be. I Can Remember Being A Young Boy Judging You Because I Had No Way Of Understanding What You Went Thru and Why We Weren’t Better Than We Were. Your Spirit Was So Soft and Kind, Regardless Of Your Struggles, You Always Had Words Of Encouragement For Me and We Always Had a Good Laugh. I Remember Sharing With You How Excited I Was To Become A Husband and A Father To My Son, and You Said “I Know You’re Doing A Great Job”. That Meant The World To Me and It’s A Moment I’ll Never Forget. You Met My Wife and She Was Able To See Where I Get My Gentle Spirit From. I Wish That We Had More Time To Develop A Stronger Relationship But I’m Thankful for The Interactions and I Know That God Will Grant You A Space In Heaven Where Your Kind Spirit Belongs. No More Suffering and No More Struggle. Fly High and Watch Over Me and Aisha. We Will Need To Feel Your Gentle Spirit As We Continue To Navigate Our Way Thru Life. PS: I Really Meant It, When I Said I Ain’t Mad Atcha. Love You JP. Until We Meet Again 😢

Year After Year, “My Wife” Just Gets Finer. I Am Excited To Celebrate You Today-Tomorrow and Beyond. You Are An Amazing Woman, Who Deserves Every Good Thing That Life Has To Offer. I Love You and I’m Happy To Share These Great Pics and Moments We Have Shared Together!! I Am Screaming Happy Birthday To Wife All The Way Across The World. I Hope That You Have An Amazing Weekend. Love You Much!
